_sText:
This is a map of Tesco's, CTs start at the back of the store and Terrorists start at the entrance.  Features include:

Hidden room with weapons
Included Nav file
Gun in a cash register
Cafe
Pharmacist counter
Many aisles
Vegetable aisles where you can hide in the vegetables
Fridges which open and a few empty ones where you can hide or pick up a weapon
Way onto the roof if you work as a team to get someone in vent
Toilets with condom machine (lol)
Automatic doors
2 entrances but many ways in
Bakery
Working fire alarm & a fire exit door
Many custom textures Pakratted into the map
Clipping around the map so players can't walk off the edge


Focus is the inside of the shop, but you can go around the outside of the shop and go in the shop through the windows.
